title: Ebro In The Morning - White Ish Wednesday + Ebro Wants To Talk To Mayor Eric Adams
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/26/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio - Ebro is interested in talking with the Mayor of New York City - Eric Adams.

The crew plays "White Ish Wednesday," Cardi B wins a defamation lawsuit, the MLB Hall of Fame snubbed some legends and the gurus give advice! All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
